Description: Microsoft Azure IoT device SDK for C Library, Twilio edition.
 The Microsoft Azure IoT device libraries for C contain code that
 facilitates building devices and applications that connect to and
 are managed by Azure IoT Hub services. Includes Twilio's patches for
 Trust Onboard.

